org.opensha2.calc

Interface NamedLocation

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NehrpTestCity, NshmpSite

    public interface NamedLocation
    Marker interface for enums of Locations. This interface is distinct from Named due to shadowing of Enum.name(). Typically, implementating enum types return a human-readable label via toString() and return the value typically returned by Enum.name() via id() .
    Author:
    Peter Powers
